                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00112 European War 1939/2482: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Beirut</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Engert</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-04-18T12:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 18, 1941—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>55. Your 101, April 8, 10 a.m. The Treasury Department regards the arrangement
                    indicated in the Department’s telegram 51, April 5, 8 p.m. as being presently in
                    effect and is taking action to license the establishment of the special account
                    with the Chase National Bank in the name of the Banque de Syrie et du Liban,
                    which account will be designated Special Account A.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
